ad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"489309d5f874c39fafced3dab37058ff68d09465","tid":340654,"uid":67302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T00:37:25.000Z","msg":"聽過乜叫殺雞取卵未？"},{"pid":"36103c0140446ec9eb89862dd110f7642cc293b0","tid":340654,"uid":64648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T00:39:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小弟黎緊諗住睇樓，第一次買自住，都唔撚理黎緊會爆定唔爆啦<br />\n可唔可以簡單總結，買左1000萬既樓，就算跌到500萬，總統府我每月準時還錢就OK?</blockquote><br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12b6bc59277fe9d3a7eee0af0f36fde2bc5f0776","tid":340654,"uid":47147,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T00:39:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d6997dfd32680864aa2711edad99dae60dcb0446","tid":340654,"uid":47147,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T00:41:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"02f73d0780517ede7bbb23f73b5e3b95db8ddd8a","tid":340654,"uid":111571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T00:41:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"31486d0693219cc9dba8900fc8e0c9d75c5fc01b","tid":340654,"uid":47147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T00:44:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"af60c7b7bf8203bf84cf10f7061f75cb08d13b88","tid":340654,"uid":128568,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T00:45:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>小弟黎緊諗住睇樓，第一次買自住，都唔撚理黎緊會爆定唔爆啦<br />\n可唔可以簡單總結，買左1000萬既樓，就算跌到500萬，總統府我每月準時還錢就OK?</blockquote><br />\n第一 1000萬樓要做1半首期<br />\n<br />\n咁你即係有500萬係層樓度<br />\n<br />\n咁1000萬跌500萬就未負資產 <br />\n<br />\n如果跌6成 即係層樓值400萬 但你差銀行500萬<br />\n<br />\n咁就係負資產<br />\n<br />\n同埋銀行要你提早還果d通常都係做1成按揭果d<br />\n<br />\n因為佢知你有2按 驚你還唔到<br />\n<br />\n即係冇2按既話銀行係唔會call</blockquote><br />\ncall loan 極少發生，97嗰時聽人講call loan 係因為間樓幾按，怕比第間銀行搶先一步所以先call"},{"pid":"2cba1ef636f48ea79c210a298245a73782afe384","tid":340654,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-